":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T05:45:40.000Z","msg":"你地諗清楚先好做<br />\n對暴政同對平民兩樣野黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a9ca22f22306ccd0f9a1d4ecea9c117bf814a8b","tid":1359130,"uid":199907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T05:48:57.000Z","msg":"要諗下你地同元朗班白衣暴徒既分別"},{"pid":"9733f9cc4342135c3b8d527c99392a79f0533b08","tid":1359130,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T06:23:02.000Z","msg":"727 和理優 不入村 不開波 會還拖<br />\n<br />\n帶齊裝備 齊上齊落！<br />\n<br />\n請大家宣傳 ！ <br />\n<br />\n行動必須謹慎<br />\n請以大局為重<br />\n用破壞去宣洩憤怒 係呢一刻絕不理智"},{"pid":"31c71cacb1b3554fc5338db7398053051ffe7fae","tid":1359130,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T06:31:09.000Z","msg":"727 和理優 不入村 不開波 會還拖<br />\n<br />\n帶齊裝備 齊上齊落！<br />\n<br />\n請大家宣傳 ！ <br />\n<br />\n行動必須謹慎<br />\n請以大局為重<br />\n用破壞去宣洩憤怒 係呢一刻絕不理智<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01a26ddba643863988adca8dd5f87f99068f202d","tid":1359130,"uid":254594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T06:36:27.000Z","msg":"政府拒絕回應五大訴求 加上元朗恐襲 足證港共已經無法保護市民<br />\n恐襲陰霾令好多人開始連和平遊行都唔敢出<br />\n香港人連遊行自由、免於恐懼既自由都無埋<br />\n現在自發不合作運動 希望透過和平手法逼政府回應<br />\n避免每星期遊行流血衝突收場<br />\n<br />\n不合作運動係透過合法增加政府管治成本、商界營運成本<br />\n從而令佢地對政府施壓<br />\n<br />\n每一次不合作其實都只係阻左大家一陣<br />\n相比港鐵一次延誤實在係小巫見大巫<br />\n雖然有好多人會受牽連<br />\n但市民都會明白 如果黑社會問題不被正視，遺禍更大<br />\n<br />\n我地和理非無辦法同黑社會正面衝突，只有透過非常手段去逼政府 逼警察正常執法<br />\n只要政治問題解決 不合作運動自然無以為繼<br />\n黑社會威脅大定失業威脅大 我諗大眾市民會識得判斷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>最後想講 7/25 7:30 九龍塘 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/mtr723\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fmtr723&d=WWcUXgYU4baXfieBSZbTe3lPKE5%2BvOhv5kPCmhOEeDs%3D&h=9e59dff1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/mtr723</a></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cdQeDqE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcdQeDqE.jpg&h=fce13e3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jv1p0D0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJv1p0D0.jpg&h=c3cf913d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LWY7YqF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLWY7YqF.jpg&h=a7a36c51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pSQm2Sm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpSQm2Sm.jpg&h=5b380ba2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VJ2TS2R.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVJ2TS2R.png&h=05aaecf9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DyzbD2D.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDyzbD2D.png&h=b1d377b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><a href=\"http://t.me/mtr723\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fmtr723&d=WWcUXgYU4baXfieBSZbTe3lPKE5%2BvOhv5kPCmhOEeDs%3D&h=9e59dff1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/mtr723</a></strong></span>"}]}